Package: fonts-apple-color-emoji
Architecture: all
Depends: fontconfig
Description: Apple Color Emoji as CBDT/CBLC TTF for Linux
 Brings Apple's vibrant color emojis to Linux. Installs the font
 and a fontconfig snippet (50-apple-color-emoji.conf) so Apple Color
 Emoji is preferred for emoji, serif, sans-serif, and monospace.
